description:
Welcome to the placeholder for Novembers SWmobile event

We're still finalising our venue and speakers but wanted to get this in the diary so you can RSVP.

Timings
18:30 Doors, Food & Drink
19:00 Intro and Talks 1&2
19:45 Break
20:00 Talks 3&4
20:45 Tidy up & Head to a local pub to continue the conversation

As always we welcome new speakers. Please message the lead organiser or any of the other organisers if you have a talk idea, or fill out the form at http://cfp.swmobile.org
title: November Talk Night
